column5: Last night I was talking to a young good looking women  She asked me if I prefer legs or breasts  I told her what I really wanted was a shaved thinggy.  Unfortunitly, I am no longer welcome at KFC  That one I had to share

Pretty sure I saw all of that on my downtown walks today!!!  #2 was presented to me right on the counter top at W Burger Barn. I was a gentleman and turned around while she put them back in her top. (I won't say how long it took to turn around)
